               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Kiros (fols. 3r-40r).</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="3r" to="40r"/>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1468GadlaK">Gadla Kiros “Vita of Kiros”</title>
                     <note>- Most probably the Ms. was copied from<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESap018">AP-018</ref>. So far, it has been established that both Mss. share
                        common errors. Also, there are no errors in A-018 which are not in<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESap017">AP-017</ref>, whereas<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESap017">AP-017</ref>has some additional errors peculiar to
                        itself (e.g. dittography on <locus target="#4va">4va, l. 1-3)</locus>.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
               </msContents>
