                  <provenance>The names Gabra Madḫǝn, Walatta Māryām, Gabra
                     Śǝllāse, ʾAmata Mikāʾel are written in the supplication formula on <locus target="#3ra">3ra</locus>. Other names, perhaps of the family members,
                     ʾAmata Giyorgis, Gabra Madḫǝn, Gabra Masqal, Walda Śǝllāse, Gabra ʾƎgziabǝher,
                     Walatta Giyorgis, Walatta Ṣādǝqān, Ḫāyla Śǝllāse, Gabra Māryām, Walatta Śǝllāse
                     are written in the supplication formula on <locus target="#40ra">40ra</locus>.</provenance>
               </history>
